{
  "stem": "20021.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then he was also on the committee which was providing coal for poor people to heat during the winter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have a book which was published by the Jews of Tarnow after the war about Tarnow and the community and all that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could maybe show it to your if you're interested.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a very-- that's thick a book.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- it really documents the life, the activities of that town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father is mentioned in the book many times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we were relatively large community, so we had practically-- we had a Jewish club for ping pong.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a Jewish sports club for soccer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a lot of activities, lots of friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not come much in contact with the Gentile community in Poland, for a number of reasons, which I can go into later if you wish.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- so we were sort of a self-contained community very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had everything, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had good schools.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I went to both of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had lots of activities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by and large, it was a happy community, I have to say, although there were many poor people too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's-- not-- not to forget about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But Tarnow was-- was the center for garment industry, which supplied clothes for-- ready-made clothes for all of Poland, you know, and also had other industries, like my father's and others.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And was a lot-- a very strong Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Most-- most Jews in Tarnow with a few exceptions were very strongly Zionist, committed to Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My two aunts went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My uncle went to Israel 1920, very early.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my great-grandfather, after whom I am named, went to visit in 1870, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
